# jemdoc: menu{MENU}{Tables.html}, title{Tables}, showsource
= Tables

Jemdoc supports creating tables using a specific block syntax.

- *Jemdoc Syntax*:
~~~
{}{Table}
\~~~
{}{table}{my-table}
Header 1 | Header 2 | Header 3 ||
Row 1, Col 1 | Row 1, Col 2 | Row 1, Col 3 ||
Row 2, Col 1 | Row 2, Col 2 | Row 2, Col 3
\~~~
~~~

- *Display*:
~~~
{}{table}{my-table}
Header 1 | Header 2 | Header 3 ||
Row 1, Col 1 | Row 1, Col 2 | Row 1, Col 3 ||
Row 2, Col 1 | Row 2, Col 2 | Row 2, Col 3
~~~
